<p>

<b>Charles Gray</b> (<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../793/1793.xml">
August 29</link> <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../674/34674.xml">
1928</link> - <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../042/18935042.xml">
